products.title: Lumiere Unlined Ahisma Luxe Faux Silk Rose Gold Roman Blind
products.metadescription: Create a space you can simply relax in, while still being super stylish too, with the lumiere ahisma luxe faux silk rose gold roman blind.    The chic rose gold colour is sure to be a hit in your home and the stunning, shimmering silk finish creates a little bit of glamour. Team
